# Exclude standalone container services from the Vercel build context.
# With "Bring your Dockerfile to Vercel Functions", Vercel auto-detects
# Dockerfile.vercel and tries to provision containers, which times out on the
# free plan (BUILD_FAILED: "Resource provisioning timed out"). These services
# are deployed/hosted separately; the Vercel project only builds the Next.js app.
backend/
directus/
